To run tests
-------------

bundle exec rspec spec

or add this alias to the your command line profile (e.g. ~/.bash_profile) and save yourself some typing:

alias runspec="bundle exec rspec spec --color"

Generate Documentation
----------------------
rdoc --exclude spec --main lib/assembly.rb

Prerequisites
--------------
Kakadu Software Binaries - for JP2 generation
    http://www.kakadusoftware.com/
    Install the Kakadu demonstration applications.

Imagemagick 6.5 or higher (with libtiff, lcms2, libjasper)
	Mac users:
	brew install imagemagick
	
exiftool http://www.sno.phy.queensu.ca/~phil/exiftool/
	Mac users:
	brew install exiftool 

Perl
